00:08:08.439 --> 00:08:13.319
And speaking of widows, wars compounded the
problem by creating lots of them, like in

00:08:13.319 --> 00:08:17.239
Europe, the Thirty Years War led to a rise
in the number of households headed by women.

00:08:17.239 --> 00:08:21.779
Women also took the lead in reducing the number
of mouths to feed by delaying marriage. Like,

00:08:21.779 --> 00:08:25.059
whenever bread prices rise, rates of marriage
fall.

00:08:25.059 --> 00:08:27.989
And the last thing that I'll mention here
is that bad weather and poor harvests also

00:08:27.989 --> 00:08:32.120
prompted migration. Like, in the first half
of the seventeenth century, perhaps one half

00:08:32.120 --> 00:08:38.100
of all adult Scotsmen left Scotland. Many
Chinese left for the Philippines, Indonesia, and Taiwan.

00:08:38.190 --> 00:08:42.339
So, we have a world that's dramatically different
because of the climate change of the Little

00:08:42.339 --> 00:08:46.959
Ice Age. Women head more households, many
communities are more ethnically diverse, population

00:08:46.959 --> 00:08:51.350
growth slowed dramatically, and there was
widespread political unrest and wars and starvation.

00:08:51.350 --> 00:08:55.180
And, of course, looking at the history of
the Little Ice Age is relevant for us today

00:08:55.180 --> 00:08:59.420
as we face a change in climate and the extreme
weather that comes with it.

00:08:59.420 --> 00:09:02.690
Sometimes, we like to imagine that math and
science don't really have much to do with

00:09:02.690 --> 00:09:07.329
the humanities, that, like, how we live in
the world isn't really shaped by our environment.

00:09:07.329 --> 00:09:12.400
But, of course, it is. We are shaping our
environment. Our environment is also shaping us.

00:09:12.470 --> 00:09:16.730
To end on a hopeful note, the agricultural
innovations that developed in the face of

00:09:16.730 --> 00:09:21.480
tremendous weather-related challenges should
remind us that it is possible to adapt to

00:09:21.480 --> 00:09:25.600
changing climates if we make the effort and
take the time. We don't know what the cast

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:29.519
iron plows of the future are going to be,
